Function Reference/recurse dirsize « WordPress Codex
-----------

Get the size of a directory recursively.

Used by
[get\_dirsize()](/Function_Reference/get_dirsize "Function Reference/get dirsize")
to get a directory's size when it contains other directories.

Usage
-----

` <?php recurse_dirsize( $directory ); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$directory` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Directory to recurse
    Default: *None*

Return Value
------------

 `` `(integer)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The size of the directory

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

Change Log
----------

Since: [MU](/Version_MU "Version MU")

Source File
-----------

`recurse_dirsize()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

